+// SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-2.0+
+/*
+ * DA7280 Haptic device driver
+ *
+ * Copyright (c) 2018 Dialog Semiconductor.
+ * Author: Roy Im <Roy.Im.Opensource@diasemi.com>
